gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pacers 134, Jazz 118
gameRecap.excerpt: The Pacers defeated the Jazz, 134-118. Tyrese Haliburton recorded 16 points, six rebounds, and 13 assists for the Pacers, while Bennedict Mathurin added 22 points, nine rebounds, and four assists in the victory. Jordan Clarkson led all scorers with 33 points and five assists for the Jazz in the losing effort. The Pacers improve to 5-3 on the season, while the Jazz fall to 2-7.
